te credit management solution for borrowers, EnCharge empowers its members by providing impeccable service, simplicity of use, working solutions, and guaranteed security.&nbsp; The company&rsquo;s variety of tools and services allows members to have a voice when it comes to managing their credit scores and credit history.</span></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%; widows: 0; orphans: 0">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#343434" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="line-height: 18px; font-size: small;"><font color="#343434"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">EnCharge supports and enables members with a multitude of benefits, including:</span></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%; widows: 0; orphans: 0">\r\n			<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#343434" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="line-height: 18px; font-size: small;"><font color="#343434"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">Accurate credit information</span></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%; widows: 0; orphans: 0">\r\n			<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#343434" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="line-height: 18px; font-size: small;"><font color="#343434"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">A detailed and meaningful credit score</span></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 150%; widows: 0; orphans: 0">\r\n			<font class="Apple-style-span" co