(28, 'privacypolicy', 'aboutus/privacypolicy', 'Privacy Policy', '', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; mso-outline-level: 1">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><span class="Apple-style-span" style="line-height: 18px; font-family: verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(34,34,34); font-size: small; font-weight: normal">Privacy Policy</span></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><span style="font-style: normal"><b>Updated December 2009</b></span></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">Our privacy policy exceeds the industry standards required by legislation globally. If you compare our policy to any of your financial institutions, you will clearly see that protecting your data is our number one priority. One requirement of the Gramm-Leach-Bliley Financial Modernization Act of 1999, or GLB, requires financial institutions to provide customers with the ability to &quot;opt-out&quot; of information sharing. EnCharge is the only company that exceeds this policy by putting our members in control of when, who can view and for what purpose their Personal Information provided to us!</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">EnCharge is made up of people who, like you expect to be treated in an honest and open manner with no double speak or legal lingo trying to absolve a corporation of its responsibility.&nbsp;With EnCharge, we believe simple honesty is the right way to go.&nbsp;At EnCharge, We respect your privacy, and we are committed to protecting it as though it was our own, remember, we a members too, and are driven to change the industry. Please read the following to learn more about our privacy policy.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="page-break-after: avoid; widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">EnCharge Inc is a licensee of the TRUSTe Privacy Program.&nbsp;&nbsp;TRUSTe is an independent, organization whose mission is to build user&rsquo;s trust and confidence in the Internet by promoting the use of fair information practices.&nbsp;&nbsp;This privacy statement covers the Web site [siteurl].&nbsp;Because this Web site wants to demonstrate its commitment to your privacy, it has agreed to disclose its information practices and have its privacy practices reviewed for compliance by TRUSTe.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="page-break-after: avoid; widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-style: normal"><span style="font-weight: normal"><span style="background: #ffffff">If you have questions or concerns regarding this statement, you should first contact Chris Steeves] at chrissteeves@enchargeinc.com.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you do not receive acknowledgement of your enquiry or your enquiry has not been satisfactorily addressed, you should contact TRUSTe at </span></span></span></font></font></font><a href="http://watchdog.truste.com/pvr.php?page=complaint&amp;url"><font color="#669999"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-style: normal"><span style="font-weight: normal"><span style="background: #ffffff">http://watchdog.truste.com/pvr.php?page=complaint&amp;url</span></span></span></font></font></font></a><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-style: normal"><span style="font-weight: normal"><span style="background: #ffffff">=</span></span></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="page-break-after: avoid; widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">TRUSTe will then serve as a liaison with us to resolve your concerns.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">1. Making the security of information a priority</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">EnCharge &nbsp;was built with the safety of your information as our biggest priority. We use the highest levels of security available on the Internet.</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">Any confidential information entered into our website, is safely transferred in an encrypted format using Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) technology. EnCharge employees with access to customer information undergo thorough background checks.&nbsp;We use a variety of techniques to provide multiple layers of protection against network or physical intrusion. We constantly monitor our servers and physical location for unauthorized access. You will notice when you are on our website that some familiar indicators do appear in your browser to confirm the entire page is secure. These indicators include the small &quot;lock&quot; icon and the &quot;s&quot; in the Web address bar (for example, &quot;https&quot;).</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">2. Collecting information</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">We collect only the information necessary to deliver the products and services offered to our members.</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">The information we gather enables us to personalize, deliver and improve our services; manage your file as well as build your personal membership profile. We collect the following types of information from our members.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><br />\r\n	</b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">Personal Information You Provide to Us:</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">Basic personal identification, such as Date Of Birth, contact information, and full name.&nbsp;Optional information that you may provide at your discretion is; income level, education level, job title and industry and other information that at your discretion can upload to your file.&nbsp;In addition, at all times, a callers voice print is captured and stored. The Personal Information that you provide to us under our terms and conditions will be used for the purposes described in those terms and conditions.&nbsp;Please note that we never ask or want your SSN or SIN.&nbsp;Members will be required to supply their unique membership number when interacting with EnCharge.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><br />\r\n	</b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">Personal Information that may be Collected Automatically:</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">When a person calls EnCharge to set up or access an account, their voice print is captured, stored, updated, verified and is ran against the voice print data base to determine if fraud is being committed.&nbsp;A person whom commits fraud&nbsp;by misrepresenting themselves or by committing fraud against a member institution is placed in our fraud data base and denied all access to EnCharge services and if applicable, their file sealed.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><br />\r\n	</b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">E-mail Communications:</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">EnCharge does not make any solicitations of our customers via email, for our products or any other customer&#39;s products. We never ask customers to email us personal information. We will receive a confirmation when you open an account with EnCharge if your computer supports this type of program. This confirmation will supply you with information necessary to access and manage your account.&nbsp;EnCharge may use this confirmation to help ensure the timeliness and effectiveness of correspondence. We consider all email sent to our customers to be critical to the functioning of our service, and we only send email at your request, or as required by our delivery of members service(s).</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><br />\r\n	</b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">Registration</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">In order to use our service, you must first complete the registration form submitting your email address and creating a password. During registration you are required to give personal information including, but not limited to: name, mailing address, Date of Birth, Phone numbers, gender, and email address. Before an account can be created, registrants must willingly offer their voice print which will be permanently attached to their file and used to grant access to the account and verify your identity. You will receive email during the registration process detailing steps you will need to follow for completion as well as important information you will want to retain for your records.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">EnCharge, Inc. is the sole owner of the information collected on EnChargeinc.com.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><br />\r\n	</b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">Third Person Personal Information</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">If you sign up for a creditor account, you may enter third person personal information such as name, email,&nbsp;&nbsp;phone number, their password and their branch address. This information is collected so your colleagues can log onto the site also, and will not be used for any other purpose other than what it is collected for.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">Orders</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">If you purchase a product or service from us on our website order form, we request certain personally identifiable information from you on our order form. You must provide contact information (such as name, email, and shipping address).</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">We use this information for billing purposes and to fill your orders. If we have trouble processing an order, we will use this information to contact you.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><br />\r\n	</b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">Social Security Numbers</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">We DO NOT allow for SSN or SIN to be provided to EnCharge nor will we solicited SSN or SIN from any persons.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><span style="font-style: normal"><b>Supplementation of Personal Information</b></span></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">To improve the security of our service, we may need to verify your personal information when necessary by matching the information you provide to EnCharge by supplementing it against other publicly available information that we obtain from third parties. This matching is done via secure systems and/or private investigations and all your information, both that which you provide to EnCharge and that which we obtain through third parties, is held in strict confidence.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><br />\r\n	</b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">3. Managing information</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">Your privacy and the security of your data is our primary concern. Your trust is extremely important to us, and we will do everything in our power to live up to the trust you place in us. Personal Information about our customers is an important part of our business. We neither rent, trade, sell or share your Personal Information to third parties for marketing purposes, or anyone else with the exception of our service providers to process a transaction. Other then yourself and EnCharge, access to your file can only be granted by you, by your expressed permission which is authenticated using your voice and only for the expressed reason.&nbsp;For example, an employer will only be able to view a limited part of your file which will not be printable nor downloadable.&nbsp;A creditor on the other hand will have access to your complete file and only for the sole purpose of the credit being sought that one time, each additional time, will require further permission from you.&nbsp;We cannot control what those that you have been granted access to view your file does with the information; as such you are advised to review their privacy policies.&nbsp;We provide your Personal Information only with our business partners and affiliates as described herein and as otherwise specifically described in the Terms and Conditions. EnCharge employees do not have any right to use Personal Information we share with them beyond what is necessary to assist us. You hereby consent to our sharing of Personal Information for the above purposes.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">You acknowledge that any acquirer of EnCharge may continue to use your Personal Information as set forth in this policy.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">Protection of EnCharge and Others: We reserve the right to disclose your Personal Information as required by law and when we believe that disclosure is necessary to protect our rights and/or comply with a judicial proceeding, court order, or legal process served on our Website.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">Accessing my information: You can access and modify the personal information collected about you by logging into your account, selecting &ldquo;edit profile&rdquo; or &ldquo;account settings&rdquo; to update this information.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">Is personal information about me secure?</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">Your EnCharge account Personal Information is protected by a password for your privacy and security. You need to ensure unauthorized access to your account and Personal Information by selecting and protecting your password appropriately and limiting access to your computer and browser by signing off after you have finished accessing your account.&nbsp;&nbsp;We don&rsquo;t store workable credit data such as credit cards numbers in their entirety or&nbsp;SSS / SIN. Additionally, the fact that your voice print is required for a creditor to view your credit file and for a creditor to report on your file, there is very little value in someone trying to access your file. However, we still use first in class multiply layering protection, unique membership number, voice print and PIN attached to voice print,&nbsp;256 bit encryption from digicert and other methods kept private to keep your information private and deny unauthorized access.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">We follow generally accepted industry standards to protect the personal information submitted to us, both during transmission and once we receive it. No method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure, however. Therefore, while we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your personal information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">If you have any questions about security on our Website, you can contact us via the contact us section of our website.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">Technologies on the Site</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><span style="font-style: normal"><span style="font-weight: normal">A cookie is a small text file that is stored on a user&rsquo;s computer for record-keeping purposes. We do use session cookies on this site.&nbsp;&nbsp;We do not link the information we store in cookies to any personally identifiable information you submit while on our site. We also have widgets on our site. Widgets support functions that require that you disclose certain personally identifiable information given the user&#39;s choice of participation. This information is collected in many different ways such as: forms, surveys, contests, forums, subscribing or unsubscribing to mailings and correcting or updating personally identifiable information and are only used for the purpose in which they were collected. These widgets include an email a friend feature. If you choose to use our referral service to email a friend about our site, we will ask you for your friend&rsquo;s name and email address.&nbsp;&nbsp;We will automatically send your friend a one-time email inviting him or her to visit the site.&nbsp;&nbsp;We do not store this information.</span></span></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<h2 class="western" style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0.11cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">Agents/Service Providers</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></h2>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">We use other third parties such as a membership card supplier to create your membership cards. When you sign up for a membership, we will share your name, mailing address and membership number as necessary for the third party to provide manufacturing and shipping of the membership card.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;We also use a live chat service provider.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm; font-weight: normal">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff">These third parties are prohibited from using your personally identifiable information for promotional purposes.</span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;</span></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; font-style: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">Links to Other Sites</span></b></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="widows: 2; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 0cm">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="''Times New Roman'', Verdana, sans-serif" size="7"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 32px"><b><font color="#000000