(44, 'faq', 'aboutus/faq', 'FAQ', '', '<p>\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="line-height: 19px; "><b>Are you a credit reporting agency?</b></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">No. EnCharge gathers and manages borrower&rsquo;s credit files so they are protected, accurate, and available to lenders in a mutually beneficial environment.</font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>So what are you?</b></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><strong><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-weight: normal">We are</span></font></font></font></strong><strong><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-weight: normal"> </span></font></font></font></strong><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">a technology-based company redefining an industry with Credit Management Solutions. O</font></font></font><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">ur state-of-the-art</font></font></font><strong><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-weight: normal"> web-based Enterprise Credit Management Solutions</span></font></font></font></strong><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"> </font></font></font><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">offer global risk and data management services to </font></font></font><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">Financial Institutions, Lenders and Borrowers.</font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>Do you produce a credit score?</b></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%; widows: 0; orphans: 0">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">We can offer the most precise and decisive credit score, where appropriate, based upon our proprietary assessment algorithms and processes.&nbsp;In addition, we have only one credit file per member and real-time identity biometric verification systems to protect you and the borrowers from fraudsters.</font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<h1 style="line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">What is a Voice Biometric?</font></font></span></font></h1>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">In its simplest form, a Voice Biometric is the unique representation of the characteristics that make up an individual&#39;s voice. </font></font></font> </span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">Similar to a fingerprint where the various ridges, troughs and curves on a finger provide a distinct method of identification, the differing physical components of a human throat and mouth produce a unique sound which can be analyzed, measured and stored. This is known as a voiceprint.</font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>What is the score range?</b></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;">&nbsp;<font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">The credit score ranges from 300 to 900.</font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><br />\r\n	<b>If I have so much control over my credit file, can it be manipulated by another party?</b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">No. There are proprietary safety measures that maintain the integrity of your credit files. But creditors still report credit information, such as late payments. </font></font></font> </span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>What if the creditor makes an error while reporting on me?</b></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.49cm; margin-bottom: 0.49cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">EnCharge members can provide us with accurate payment confirmation information so we can contact the creditor on your behalf. &nbsp;If the creditor refuses to correct the mistake after being presented with the error-evidence, we will adjust the file and discontinue the creditors&rsquo; membership.</font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>What does it cost?</b></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">Members pay $90 annually or $899 for a lifetime membership. </font></font></font> </span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>What if my bank does not yet use your service?</b></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">You can ask them to sign up for EnCharge, as it is free of charge for them. Or, let us know and we will contact them. Or, you might consider another institution that uses EnCharge. </font></font></font> </span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>My credit file doesn&rsquo;t show any creditors. Why?</b></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">When an account is created, the credit-seeker&rsquo;s credit file starts from scratch and takes time to build. This ensures 100% error-free reporting. As membership increases, the number of creditors who subscribe increases, too.</font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>Do you ask for a Social Security Number or SIN?</b></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">No. If someone saying they represent EnCharge asks you for a social security number, record what information you can gather and let us know immediately. We will in turn notify the authorities. We use a unique membership number to identify you and will never request other identification.</font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>What if someone other than myself signs up using my ID first?</b></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">It&rsquo;s not possible. When you sign up, the account is tied to your voice print permanently. The fraudster who attempts to use your ID must use their voice to set up an account. Therefore, the file they create is maintained completely separately from yours due to the voice print. They will never be able to set up a new account.</font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>What about people who cannot speak? Are they excluded from using EnCharge?</b></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">No. A person that is unable to speak can have an EnCharge-qualified attorney&rsquo;s voice print paired with their account, giving them the control and protection they need.</font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>How long will it be before creditors use your service?</b></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">The more members we have subscribing to EnCharge, the more creditors will be attracted to our service. As credit-seekers subscribe to EnCharge, creditors will want to use the accuracy and risk management solution that we provide.</font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>Why&nbsp;does&nbsp;my credit file show a score&nbsp;of 650 when I have no creditors yet reporting?</b></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">A 650 is considered a base score and the average risk of a person without credit history. It is also the average score for most people, regardless of length of history. Most people fall into the same risk category.</font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>Can I upload my credit reports from credit reporting agencies?</b></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">Yes. You can also upload documents that matter to you.&nbsp; Examples are paystubs or other supporting documentation that a bank or institution may require. </font></font></font> </span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>Will creditors be able to view what I upload to my file?</b></font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">Yes, including your optional profile picture, which gets attach to your credit file</font></font></font><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">.</font></font></font></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000000"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><b>Do you help fix errors on credit reports from Equifax or TransUnion? </b></font></font></font> </span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000000" face="Verdana, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-weight: 900; line-height: 12px; font-size: small;"><font color="#000080"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2">No. We are not a part of these agencies.&nbsp;</font></font></font> </span></font></p>\r\n', 1);
