(45, 'membership_agreement', 'aboutus/membership_agreement', 'Terms of Membership and Membership Agreement', '', '<p>\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: small; font-weight: 800; line-height: 16px; ">Terms of Membership and Membership Agreement</span> </b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 0.37cm; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#666666"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-style: normal"><span style="font-weight: normal"><span style="background: #ffffff">The following terms and agreement govern the EnCharge Memberships and the benefits available thereunder (the &quot;EnCharge Service&quot;).&nbsp;</span></span></span></font></font></font><strong><font color="#666666"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-style: normal"><span style="font-weight: normal"><span style="background: #ffffff">ALL PERSONS SUBSCRIBING TO THE EnCharge SERVICE ARE URGED TO READ THE TERMS OF MEMBERSHIP AND MEMBERSHIP AGREEMENT CAREFULLY AND IF THERE ARE ANY QUESTIONS TO CONTACT AN EnCharge REPRESENTATIVE AT&nbsp;1-866-245-4290, 8am &ndash; 1am EST Monday - Saturday.</span></span></span></font></font></font></strong><font color="#666666"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-style: normal"><span style="font-weight: normal"><span style="background: #ffffff"> This terms of memberships and membership agreements (the &quot;Terms of Memberships and Membership Agreement,&quot; or &quot;Agreement&quot;) is made between EnCharge, Inc. (&quot;EnCharge&quot;), a Delaware corporation and the person or organization specified on the EnCharge membership card or database. (&quot;you&quot; or the &quot;member&quot;).</span></span></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.32cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#666666"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-style: normal"><span style="font-weight: normal"><span style="background: #ffffff">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></font></font></font><font color="#666666"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-style: normal"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">Description of EnCharge Membership</span></b></span></font></font></font><font color="#666666"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-style: normal"><span style="font-weight: normal"><span style="background: #ffffff">. Each Member is entitled to receive services and other benefits on specified terms. All Consumer Benefits as specified by the&nbsp;</span></span></span></font></font></font><a href="[siteurl]"><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-style: normal"><span style="font-weight: normal"><span style="background: #ffffff">[siteurl]</span></span></span></font></font></font></a><font color="#666666"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="font-style: normal"><span style="font-weight: normal"><span style="background: #ffffff">&nbsp;website and are as available. To access Consumer Members area of the Website, a Member will be required to enter his or her EnCharge Membership number or registered email address and password.</span></span></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.59cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">a.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A Member&#39;s actual savings and benefits will vary depending upon the number and or actual creditor using EnCharge service, for what purpose and the length of time of you are a Member.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.59cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">b.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;All Benefits are subject to discontinuation, change, modification, improvement or substitution without notice and EnCharge makes no representations or warranties with respect to, and accepts no responsibility or liability for, out of date or erroneous information related thereto.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.59cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">c.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The membership fees for joining EnCharge are non-refundable payable for the Member&#39;s subscription to the members&rsquo; area of the Website and are view as your endorsement of the EnCharge vision to change the credit reporting industry.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.32cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color="#666666"><b>Membership Term; Renewals</b></font><font color="#666666">. A Member shall be entitled to all of the Benefits available to Members of the EnCharge Service for the ensuing twelve-month period under the annual plan, commencing on the date of acceptance of the Member&#39;s application for enrolment for each twelve-month period thereafter (the &quot;Membership Term&quot;). EnCharge reserves the right to change the terms and conditions of this Agreement at any time, and may cancel this Agreement or the EnCharge Service.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.32cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color="#666666"><b>Membership Term; Lifetime</b></font><font color="#666666">. A Member shall be entitled to all of the Benefits available to Members of the EnCharge Service for the life of the member under the lifetime plan, commencing on the date of acceptance of the Member&#39;s application for enrolment for the lifetime membership thereafter (the &quot;Membership Term&quot;). EnCharge reserves the right to change the terms and conditions of this Agreement at any time, and may cancel this Agreement or the EnCharge Service.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.32cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color="#666666"><b>Electronic Disclosure and Consent</b></font><font color="#666666">. Your payment for the membership shall constitute your consent to receive any and all disclosures, notices and other communications including any notice that may be legally required to be provided to you regarding this Agreement, in electronic form. EnCharge will provide all future disclosures and notices by sending an alert to the electronic mail address that you have provided.&nbsp;<br />\r\n	At your request, EnCharge agrees to provide you with a paper copy of any amendments to this Agreement but EnCharge will charge you a processing fee and a shipping fee for such service. You may request paper copies of required notices by calling 1-866-245-4290.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.59cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">a.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You have the right to withdraw this consent, but if you do EnCharge will immediately terminate this Agreement and/or the EnCharge Service. To withdraw your consent, please contact EnCharge by calling 1-866-245-4290.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.59cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">b.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In order for you to access and retain this information, your system must meet the following requirements: (1) An PC or Macintosh compatible computer, (2) Internet Access, (3) An Internet browser such as Internet Explorer 4.0 or above, or another such equivalent Internet browser. In order for you to print or download disclosures you must have a printer connection from your PC or sufficient hard-drive space available to save the disclosures. If these software or hardware requirements change, EnCharge will provide you with prior notice of such change and the opportunity to withdraw your consent via electronic mail. Your submission of an online application shall constitute your acknowledgement that you have access to the software and hardware necessary to receive via electronic means these disclosures and notice of any changes to the software and hardware requirements.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.59cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">c.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;It is your responsibility to contact EnCharge immediately if your electronic or postal mail address changes. You can contact EnCharge to inform EnCharge of such changes through the website.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.32cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color="#666666"><b>EnCharge Annual Membership Fee; Renewal Fees</b></font><font color="#666666">. The current EnCharge membership fee (the &quot;Membership Fee&quot;) will only be automatically billed to Member&#39;s designated credit card account or other authorized billing source (e.g. debit card) on an annual recurring basis as authorized by you. This authorization is given by clicking the renew box on your profile page anytime before expiration date. Any Member who uses a debit card as the designated credit card account acknowledges that&nbsp;</font><font color="#666666"><b>EnCharge will not be responsible for any fees or penalties associated with insufficient funds, bounced checks or any other form of fee due to a charge of the Annual Member Fee to a debit card provided by the Member</b></font><font color="#666666">.&nbsp;</font><font color="#666666"><b>Right to update Credit Card Account Information</b></font><font color="#666666">. If the credit card provided by Member to EnCharge has expired during an attempt to bill fees per section 4, EnCharge will revise the expiration date and proceed with billing using the same credit card account.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.32cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color="#666666"><b>Right to Cancel; Refund of EnCharge Membership Fee</b></font><font color="#666666">. Members have the right to terminate this Agreement and membership with EnCharge at any time. A Member may cancel this Agreement and membership by calling 1-866-245-4290. If a Member cancels before the end of a Membership Term for which Member has paid, the Member cannot receive a refund of such Membership Fee, prorated for the remaining unused portion of the Membership Term. Due to the nature of the services provided by EnCharge (many of which are accessible immediately upon acceptance) it is understood that refunds cannot be issued. Member will remain liable for any other fees or charges to be paid pursuant to this Agreement.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.32cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color="#666666"><b>Disclaimer of Liability</b></font><font color="#666666">. Vendors. EnCharge shall have no liability in regard to any services provided, or to be provided, by any affiliates, non-affiliated third party sponsor, affiliate, creditor members or vendor (&quot;Vendor&quot;) and are considered independent from EnCharge or contractors and not employees, partners or joint venture partners with EnCharge. EnCharge shall have no liability in regard to any Benefits provided, or to be provided, by any Vendor. You agree that claims with regard to services shall be made against the Vendor providing or performing such services and not EnCharge. Although EnCharge upon request by the member, will endeavour to intervene in conjunction with a member experiencing a problem or discrepancy with a Vendor, in the event any product or service purchased by a Member is cancelled, modified, defective, or otherwise unsatisfactory to the Member, the Member will look solely to the provider, seller, merchant or manufacturer of the product or service for any satisfaction of claim.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.32cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color="#666666"><b>EnCharge Member Representation and Obligations</b></font><font color="#666666">. Each Member acknowledges such Member&#39;s obligations to EnCharge as follows: (a) you have read the &quot;Terms of Membership and Membership Agreement&quot; carefully, and understand the provisions of the EnCharge Service and the billing method for the payment of the annual Service Fee; (b) You may cancel your membership with EnCharge at any time prior to the conclusion of the then current Membership Term and will not be entitled to a refund of the prorate unused portion of the Service Fee,</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.32cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">9.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color="#000000">You agree that you will not use the Site for any purpose that is unlawful or not permitted by this Agreement. By way of example, and not as a limitation, you agree that when uploading to or communicating via the Site, or phone with an EnCharge representative, including in respect of any forums, chat-rooms or other exchanges (a &ldquo;Forum&rdquo;) accessed on or through the Site, you shall not do any of the following:</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.54cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#000000">a.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Defame, abuse, harass, stalk, threaten or otherwise violate the legal rights (such as rights of privacy) of others.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.54cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-top: 0.05cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#000000">b.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Publish, post, distribute or disseminate any defamatory, infringing, obscene, pornographic, sexual, indecent or unlawful material or information.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.54cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-top: 0.05cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#000000">c.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Upload or otherwise transfer files that contain software or other material protected by intellectual property laws (or by rights of privacy or confidentiality) unless you own or control the rights thereto or have received all necessary consents.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.54cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-top: 0.05cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#000000">d.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Upload or otherwise transfer files that contain viruses, corrupted files or any other similar software or programs that may damage or inhibit the operation of another computer.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.54cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-top: 0.05cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#000000">e.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Delete any author attributions, legal notices, or proprietary designations or labels in any file that is uploaded.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.54cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-top: 0.05cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#000000">f.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Falsify the origin or source of software or other material contained in a file that is uploaded.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.54cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-top: 0.05cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#000000">g.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Offer to sell any goods or services or conduct or forward surveys, contests or chain letters.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.54cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-top: 0.05cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#000000">h.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Download any file posted by another user of a Forum that you know, or reasonably should know, cannot be legally distributed in such manner.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.54cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-top: 0.05cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#000000">i.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Use any communications or Content or other information obtained through the Site in a manner that is competitive with the Site or EnCharge&rsquo;s business.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.54cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-top: 0.05cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#000000">j.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Knowingly make false statements or false notes or your file or to an EnCharge representative.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.54cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-top: 0.05cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#000000">k.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Inhibit EnCharge to make corrections to any errors on your credit file.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.54cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-top: 0.05cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#000000">l.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Attempt to create multiple accounts</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 2.54cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-top: 0.05cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#000000">m.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Attempt to commit fraud</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.27cm; text-indent: 0.05cm; margin-top: 0.05cm; margin-bottom: 0.05cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666"><b>A violation of this provision will result in your forfeiture of membership with EnCharge, potential legal action from EnCharge and its Vendors</b></font><font color="#666666">; and (e) EnCharge assumes no responsibility for the payment of or contribution to any use or sales tax on Benefits that may be imposed by any state or federal taxing authority and such taxes, to the extent imposed, shall remain the sole responsibility of the Member or the direct provider of the Benefits, as the case may be.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.32cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">10.&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color="#666666"><b>Governing Law; Arbitration</b></font><font color="#666666">. This Agreement, and the respective rights and obligations of the parties hereunder, shall be governed by, and construed in accordance with, the laws of the State of Delaware. Any dispute arising between you and EnCharge will be submitted to arbitration in the State of Delaware in accordance with the rules of the American Arbitration Association then in effect. Nothing herein stated shall deprive you of the benefits of your state&#39;s consumer protection laws.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.32cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-sp