ass="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">12.&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color="#666666"><b>General Release</b></font><font color="#666666">. Each Member, for himself/herself, and on behalf of any person who uses the Benefits available through the EnCharge Membership (&quot;Membership Beneficiary&quot;), hereby forever releases, acquits and discharges EnCharge from any and all liabilities, claims, demands, actions and causes of action that such Member or such Member&#39;s legal representatives may have by reason of any monetary damage or personal injury sustained as a result of or during the use of any and all Benefits available through EnCharge. The sole recourse available to a Member, Membership Beneficiary or their legal representatives shall be the cancellation of the Membership.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.32cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font color="#222222"><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><span style="background: #ffffff"><font color="#666666">13.&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color="#666666"><b>Entire Agreement</b></font><font color="#666666">. The foregoing Terms of Membership and Membership Agreement contain the entire terms and agreements in connection with Member&#39;s participation with EnCharge and no representations, inducements, promises or agreement, or otherwise, between EnCharge and the Member not included herein, shall be of any force or effect. If any of the foregoing terms or provisions shall be invalid or unenforceable, the remaining terms and provisions hereof shall not be affected thereby.</font></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 1.32cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; line-height: 0.37cm; widows: 2; orphans: 2">\r\n	<font class="Apple-style-span" color="#666666" face="verdana, sans-serif" size="3"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 14px;"><b><font face="Verdana, sans-serif"><font size="2"><font color="#666666"><span style="font-style: normal"><span style="font-weight: normal"><span style="background: #ffffff">14.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></font><font color="#666666"><span style="font-style: normal"><b><span style="background: #ffffff">Binding Effect</span></b></span></font><font color="#666666"><span style="font-style: normal"><span style="font-weight: normal"><span style="background: #ffffff">. The foregoing Terms of Membership and Membership Agreement shall be binding upon and inure to the benefit of EnCharge and the Member.</span></span></span></font></font></font></b></span></font></p>\r\n', 1),
