(58, 'creditorsignupemailt', 'aboutus/creditorsignupemailtemplate', 'Creditor Signup Email Template', '', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="background-image: url([siteurl]/images/email_bg.jpg); padding-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(142,157,197); padding-left: 10px; width: 700px; padding-right: 10px; font-family: calibri,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; height: 500px; color: rgb(255,255,255); font-size: 14px; padding-top: 30px">\r\n	<h4 style="text-align: center; color: rgb(0,51,153); font-size: 16px">\r\n		A Credit Reporting Management Company</h4>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Thank you for choosing <span style="color: rgb(192,0,0)">En</span>Charge and welcome to your first day of true Credit Empowerment.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Your Membership number is [ memberno ]</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		At your convenience, go to <a href="[siteurl]" target="_blank">[siteurl]/</a> to start using the tools your account offers and start protecting your institution from fraud and unnecessary expenses.<br />\r\n		In order to access your account, please enter your membership number as well as the password you created during the sign-up process in the members login field.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		We are delighted to have you as a member. Feel free to contact us at <span style="text-decoration: underline">1-866-245-4290</span> if you have any concerns or questions. We will be working hard to continually improve our service and the value that we can bring to you and your organization.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Once again, Thank you for joining <span style="color: rgb(192,0,0)">En</span>Charge in its fight to change the Industry. Together we will make history.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Please, remember to tell your friends and colleagues about us and feel free to contact us at anytime. We look forward to serving you for many years to come.</p>\r\n	<div style="margin-top: 90px">\r\n		<div style="float: left">\r\n			Best Regards,<br />\r\n			Wayne Berry<br />\r\n			Founder of <span style="color: rgb(192,0,0)">En</span>Charge<br />\r\n			&ldquo